{"tid":2120134,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"英國公布BNO持有人和家屬","createTime":"2020-07-22T13:10:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-22T13:35:17.000Z","uid":281029,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b63a8bf09ca87ab44c0069278483ace3b37e5f2c","tid":2120134,"uid":281029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T13:10:29.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\">【有線新聞】英國公布BNO持有人和家屬，定居和入籍安排。<br />\n持有BNO的港人和家屬，不論是否在英國境內，明年1月起可申請入境並留在英國30個月，之後再申請延長多30個月。又或一次過留在英國5年。申請者可以工作和讀書，但不會享有社會福利。住滿5年後，可以申請定居英國。住多一年後便可申請英藉。<br />\n申請者不必持有有效的BNO護照，過期或遺失了BNO的港人都可以申請。<br />\n另需證明在經濟上，可支持到自己和家屬在英國生活6個月，並展示出願意學習英語等。<br />\n<a href=\"https://ott-news.i-cable.com/en-us/l/open-content?cid=31009&amp;ct=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fott-news.i-cable.com%2Fen-us%2Fl%2Fopen-content%3Fcid%3D31009%26ct%3D1&d=DosFxDX7yTzXLN9Gri3QgHljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=50b3016a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ott-news.i-cable.com/en-us/l/open-content?cid=31009&amp;ct=1</a></span>"},{"pid":"2ab3eb5f4eb50a148084e2872953ce230afbde1b","tid":2120134,"uid":78394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T13:33:40.000Z","msg":"續都唔洗續？"},{"pid":"57b804327f4fceaaaeceb22e422c632bae6500ad","tid":2120134,"uid":231957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T13:34:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0903096c29877e16913c1f3079850dd21554573","tid":2120134,"uid":231957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T13:35:17.000Z","msg":"thank you<br />\n<br />\n而家 要立克同屋企人講左<br />\n<br />\n可能就開戰  要走了"}]}